The paper also involves optimization and decision-making, which could place it in the cs.CC (Computational Complexity) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) categories. The use of ordered indices and modular arithmetic suggests a connection to algorithms and data structures, which could place it in the cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) category.
